{"tid":1434251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家醒下唔好比班分化撚洗腦","createTime":"2019-08-08T17:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T03:22:05.000Z","uid":292497,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"cff539a8c4ed87df41ff08f310b3c2e7310cbdd6","tid":1434251,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:11:47.000Z","msg":"自從5/8開始連登成堆post都係到係咁屌勇武作用不大唔好再勇武轉場齋和理非咁 但係有好多正評<br />\n做乜撚野ja 唔係分化但屌齋和理非係work ge 一早2014就得左啦<br />\n<br />\n我唔係話齋勇武會work 甚至我身邊一d藍變綠既人都會話有d前線手段 佢會有反感<br />\n<br />\n但屌你啦 成堆post係咁係到貶低勇武<br />\n有個post仲搞笑話咩 612 71唔係靠勇武<br />\n唔係靠勇武唔通靠你9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n家下不嬲和理非勇武雙線一齊行先可以捱到宜家<br />\n班仆街咪撚分化好無 比意見絕對有用 但咪撚係到貶低任何一邊既付出或者想霸大台<br />\n<br />\n不過我個人都認同前線有時唔洗下下都出大技<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終好多人都未完全接受 不過點撚樣都唔割<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"3ff68088e3f9567a6810f511ed91028828cd698b","tid":1434251,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:18:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d46d96a501088a00a545f1ce14aac956d6f8327","tid":1434251,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:20:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45a539894e85d130d84689cdba43daa7ef35be43","tid":1434251,"uid":303110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:23:46.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7b039252b86e4df7256aac7cb5e077b236f3ded5","tid":1434251,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:28:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"006c0da01853c6e7e64ddaba9c034f86a7f9666e","tid":1434251,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T17:31:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efbf1dfd8f92d1fb5c81ae4c49ddc3977e977046","tid":1434251,"uid":209689,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"勇武是唯一出路！起大台、和理非主義全割席"},{"pid":"17f1762792b1794e5aea7635067b8b72564cab92","tid":1434251,"uid":277560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:13:35.000Z","msg":"[心理戰] 唔好再講和理非 唔好再講勇武<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1427484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1427484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b32a4fb295effee7f2362a8a9170860722b1bc51","tid":1434251,"uid":54708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:14:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2362236ca3836c92f3b9cfc77d607a42c634daf7","tid":1434251,"uid":90704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:17:15.000Z","msg":"咁耐以黎勇武一直都只用相對武力<br />\n班仆街斬人捉到都冇打撚死佢<br />\n<br />\n前線要面對持刀兇徒警犬武警老解<br />\n而且非常be water <br />\n智勇雙全<br />\n<br />\n完全唔明點解日日失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502f7de301b1e2fc8ab61e230ec4996cb43e72d8","tid":1434251,"uid":215341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:17:54.000Z","msg":"記住我地要爭取嘅嘢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷至今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、 成立獨立調查委員會，徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選</span>"},{"pid":"033680effbd8cbd447bf6b5d724a1d3eed6a3bea","tid":1434251,"uid":270398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T18:23:23.000Z","msg":"正確出路係全方位升級, 唔理你咩勇武和理非(其實大家最好開始少用呢D字眼), 上前線親自行動攻政府建築/同狗+黑幫+政府正面對抗根本就係一定要KEEP住做既事, 同時又一邊以所有可能既非正面衝突手段威脅共匪(罷工/經濟戰等等)先係正路"},{"pid":"c30de6ffbe578904e503b27c28bc2e18e03a5a7c","tid":1434251,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:22:05.000Z","msg":"推"}]}